"Inspeccionar Corrupcion: Naberius":
"An unexplained phenomenon has changed
the environment in a region of Naberius.
Abnormal changes in the native species
have also been confirmed.

ARKS are to dispatch and discover the
cause of this \"corrupted area\".
――――――――――――――――――――
Reune [2000] Puntos de mision para completar."
